VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'a resource like GDScript. Now you\'re going to notice before in GDAU you had like 2D 3D script and so on. Well, how does that work now? Well, it works in a couple of ways. Let\'s get rid of this for for a second. So here, this one, for'

