[02:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'go with, but that\'s how you toggle between the 2D and 3D versions of a scene. Very straightforward. Now, what about assets? Well, assets uh basically are given the first class window treatment as well. So, let\'s just say I have uh this shader right here or this'

